Kesar is one of the most popular varieties of Pomegranates in India.

Kiwi is an exotic wonder that is rich in Vitamin C and Vitamin K.

data.description: Today, the world‚Äôs largest rice producers are China, India, and Indonesia. Outside of Asia, Brazil is the largest rice producer. Rice grows in warm, wet climates.
